    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/4b71a90e63ba1491eb1a3a9a376a7399.poster.avif?t=1764925409\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/4b71a90e63ba1491eb1a3a9a376a7399.webm?t=1764925409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/4b71a90e63ba1491eb1a3a9a376a7399.mp4?t=1764925409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在 1970 年代，有一个名为威权的极端政权，因铁腕统治广为人知。他们在统治期间恶行累累，罄竹难书。但那些日子已经成为了过去，因为他们现在正渴望着加入欧盟。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/5b413020b658c98f27b872306c4ec4e8.poster.avif?t=1764925409\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/5b413020b658c98f27b872306c4ec4e8.webm?t=1764925409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/5b413020b658c98f27b872306c4ec4e8.mp4?t=1764925409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你扮演一位代号为戴斯蒙的特工，受命于威权组织，负责从奥克庄园取回和销毁机密文件，它们揭露了过去发生的许多惨剧。然而，这趟旅程将带你发掘到令人不安的秘密——阿尔法计划。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">游戏特色•<li>揭开阿尔法计划的真相，发现威权多年来一直隐藏的秘密<br></li><li>在地狱般的噩梦中幸存下来，逃离可怕的奥克森林<br></li><li>解决在任务中遇到的谜题<br></li><li>探索黑暗而迷人，且深受 70 年代中欧时期启发的氛围，</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/3cce3346d6c0a19c5ed22ab39a9fb5a9.poster.avif?t=1764925409\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/3cce3346d6c0a19c5ed22ab39a9fb5a9.webm?t=1764925409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714920/extras/3cce3346d6c0a19c5ed22ab39a9fb5a9.mp4?t=1764925409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
